name: D W E L L E R
description:
[SIMULATANEON SERIES #011]

D W E L L E R

Tiny pockets of despair punctuate the Journey. They appear to come out of thin air, and can be seen only with peripheral vision. Mostly harmless if kept in check.

SIMULATANEON is a 2017 hypersigil and a conceptual prison break map for the upcoming matrix system update. The sigils that were borrowed for this series reveal only part of a bigger tapestry.
